description:
Kate finally sends a proper thank you note to a friend who got her a gift nine years ago, and Doree gets into time management and works on saying “no”. Then they go deep into dupes! They break down their own favorites dupes and hear from listeners about the affordable products they’ve found that work just as well as pricier ones.


To leave a voicemail for a future mini-ep, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com. Everything mentioned on the show can be found on our website.


This episode is sponsored by:

  • The Testaments (US) - To learn more and to listen to audiobook clips, visit penguinrandomhouseaudio.com/testaments.
  • Native - For 20% off your first purchase just visit nativedeodorant.com and use promo code FOREVER35 at checkout!
  • Away - For $20 off a suitcase visit awaytravel.com/serums and use promo code serums at checkout.
  • ThirdLove - Go to thirdlove.com/forever to get 15% off your first purchase.
  • FIGS - For 15% off your first purchase, go to wearfigs.com and enter promo code FOREVER at checkout.


Theme music by Riot.
